speculative support and scattered selling by financial
institutions.
</P>
<P>
Dealers said that activity was low during the early session as
today was the last day of the current settlement but later most of
the deals were done on squaring up positions. Elsewhere, share
prices showed small movements either way on buying and selling.
The volume of business was low.  
