<HEADLINE> Gold Price in Hong Kong Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, June 6 (Xinhua) -- The gold price in Hong Kong today
rose 20 HK dollars to close at 3,181 HK dollars a tael, according
to Po Sang Bank, one of the major gold dealers in Hong Kong.
</P>
<P>
The gold price is equivalent to 344.81 dollars a troy ounce, up
2.11 US dollars at today's exchange rate of one US dollar to
7.7440 HK dollars. 
</P>
