<HEADLINE> Auto Parts and Components Project in East China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JINAN, June 6 (Xinhua) -- Preparations for a joint-venture auto
parts manufacturing project are underway in east China's Shandong
province, an official with China's auto industry said in the
provincial capital, Jinan.
</P>
<P>
