<TEXT>
<P>
MONTEVIDEO, June 5 (Xinhua) -- For the first time in history,
Uruguayan women have been enrolled to study at the Military
Aeronautics School, Uruguayan military sources said.
</P>
<P>
Uruguay is the third Latin American country after Chile and
Colombia to allow women to study at a military aviation school to
give them the opportunity of flying military aircraft.
</P>
